sequenceDiagram
  participant Owner as Desktop/VS Code Codex owner
  participant Pipe as codex-ipc pipe
  participant Feed as CodexIpcFeed
  participant Tracker as ThreadStreamTracker
  participant GW as WebSocketGateway
  participant Web as web/app.js

  Owner->>Pipe: thread-stream-state-changed snapshot/patch
  Pipe->>Feed: IPC broadcast frame
  Feed->>Tracker: applyBroadcast()
  Tracker-->>Feed: projection + conversationState
  Feed->>Feed: buildDesktopSurfaceSnapshot()
  Feed->>GW: event/status
  GW->>Web: codex_ipc_sync_event
  GW->>Web: conversation_surface_snapshot
  GW->>Web: conversation_status_changed
  GW->>Web: conversation_action_required
  Web->>Web: trackConversationEvent()
  Web->>Web: renderDesktopSurface / approval / PLAN / goal
